e=\"\">館長到處樹敵\n難免被暗殺\n這次是警告</code></pre><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2296813\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2296813</a><br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">    香港人玩TikTok\n    爛貨\n\n周庭利用tiktok賺錢</code></pre><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmZohghsio38D3ZREoSV2fbjBYV6pAYKtHLnrFhayEA26V?filename=ZBP31YS.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZBP31YS.png&h=0f54143f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2474533\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2474533</a><br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">    台灣人和了解台灣都無直接關係\n    正如香港人都未必了解香港\n\n所以呢？台鐵國營轉民營化與你無關</code></pre><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/aAGDAtV\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/aAGDAtV</a><br />\n9up<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">黎智英的子女都在國外\n算是中國裸官</code></pre><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2328902\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2328902</a><br />\n口號建國<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nSimonTW詞不達義之餘，亦從來唔解釋諗法。<br />\n<br />\n仲要喺眾志、肥佬黎出事落井下石、踩港，呢個人真係同路人？<br />\n<br />\n喺連登談論台鐵出軌嘅時候，又彈出嚟話唔關香港人事，仲惡過狗。<br />\n<br />\n出事就出Post做影印機洗底，難得仲有咁多人推Post、大叫港台友好，各位香港人係咪盲咗？<br />\n回應未啊台支"},{"pid":"9a1f6b776078413428bbb2ba2dd6a7d84c7fed39","tid":2488634,"uid":48631,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T11:50:24.000Z","msg":"咁其實我成日都唔明實彈演習抗議是咩意思<br />\n即是我條女俾綠帽我戴，我就即場喺佢面前打飛機射到地精抗議咁樣？🤔"},{"pid":"513f3cffc561706d5b200a754aac5923bf5c309b","tid":2488634,"uid":245441,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T11:50:26.000Z","msg":"真正射落海都唔益你"},{"pid":"864bd3cd72ddd113a94e49e615a4f77dcb08e0d9","tid":2488634,"uid":143526,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T11:51:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img 